{"tid":1025650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲 2018 第四季手機市場近三分一由中國廠商佔據","createTime":"2019-02-17T13:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T17:08:50.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6dca8e4309eb584730bb777ec55f5096220e2b4","tid":1025650,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"雖然歐洲與中國關係不是很好，不過對於消費者而言，對於便宜而功能不俗的中國手機就沒什麼抵抗力。最近一個報告發現，去年的第四季，歐洲手機市場有近三分一由中國廠商佔據。<br />\n<br />\n根據市場調查機構 Canalys 的最新數據顯示，在去年第四季，歐洲銷量最好的手機品牌是 Samsung，佔 28.7%，然後是佔 26% 的 Apple，之後就是佔 23?6% 的華為。雖然華為並非佔有率最高的廠商，但如果以國家分類，中國廠商還有排行後面的小米等等。據 Canalys 表示，中國廠商總共佔了市場的 32%，其中華為和小米的佔有率按年上升分別 55.7% 和 62%，相當驚人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/17/211540_cf9807bd88a54edafa8f641fe0b681ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F17%2F211540_cf9807bd88a54edafa8f641fe0b681ef.png&h=e7dadd07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國廠商的手機大多都是以價格優勢作賣點，在經濟放緩的歐洲吸引力更高。而近年一些廠商如華為更開始推出高階手機挑戰 Samsung 和 Apple，結果而言這些產品亦相當成功。隨著 iPhone 的銷量下跌，Canalys 預計今年華為會超越 Apple，在手機市場拿下第二名。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Verge<br />\n圖片來源：Radio NZ<br />\n<br />\n﻿ &bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=6910c401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁<a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=ff1ed11c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a><br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=8c8de8e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/02/17/chinese-phones-europe-market-share-2018/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F02%2F17%2Fchinese-phones-europe-market-share-2018%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=471e773d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/02/17/chinese-phones-europe-market-share-2018/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"85c549cb71fe069d6d4eabe9a03e59557383c375","tid":1025650,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"便宜冇用架 中國製 1年就壞<br />\ne.g 小米"},{"pid":"0c6140819d19cbce28ba7b344295f1570aa24aff","tid":1025650,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"韓國有國企<br />\n美國就唯一最大電話廠<br />\n噉淨返就梗係雜乜啦"},{"pid":"8ea3cf55da19d03fe2611c0f3eca8df37dc234c2","tid":1025650,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"大鑊<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx%2Fi%2FsWkHesT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%252Fi%252FsWkHesT.gif&h=7e77add3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02f27f8c4779ec4a5dc7e17f6ed1c652bc91e91f","tid":1025650,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"中國只會慢慢稱霸全國 <br />\n我好自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ea7fcb0acee661650844c7a30db83cf56665da","tid":1025650,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國只會慢慢稱霸全球<br />\n我好自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"071f00e0c90989748c7541bd821c9b5b8969447b","tid":1025650,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"撐samsung撐apple"},{"pid":"2dc22a8ffbd52d778fc83469cfd71532fee8725d","tid":1025650,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r